// Go workspace tying the dotvirt app module and its installer operator together,
// so editor tooling and `go build ./...` span both. The operator is a SEPARATE
// module (operator/go.mod) on purpose: controller-runtime drags in a large
// k8s.io/* dependency tree that must not constrain the app binary's KubeVirt/Argo
// client versions. It imports the app's shared pkg/forge via the replace in
// operator/go.mod (which also lets the operator build standalone, e.g. in its
// container image).
go 1.26.4

use (
	.
	./operator
)
